{
  "chapter": 12,
  "chapter_summary": "本章为\"往事如烟\"，故事发生于一处荒郊大厅内。\"神手\"战飞杀死百十只鸡威吓众人，强推裴珏为江南绿林道总瓢把子。裴珏沉浸在对檀文棋、袁泸珍、孙锦平等人的往事回忆中，对眼前之事茫然不知。\"七巧追魂\"那飞虹巧妙提醒战飞需征得裴珏本人同意，吴鸣世以手势代裴珏\"表态\"，裴珏阴差阳错点头应允。\"金鸡\"向一啼怒而出手偷袭裴珏后逃走，战飞追击未果返回，发现众人已散。战飞以恩威并施收服仆人须新，随后与七巧追魂暗中结盟，商议利用裴珏伤势控制他的计策。二人来到莫氏兄弟为裴珏疗伤之处，战飞粗暴夺走金创药。章末，一名神秘女子突然现身，冷厉喝令北斗七煞兄弟出来，悬念陡生。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_nan",
      "speaker_name": "莫南",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这位‘神手’战飞，行事真是令人莫测高深，好生生的——”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你我畅谈甚欢，这些鸡却叫得讨厌，老夫一气之下，就将它提来杀了——”",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“若还有谁敢打断老夫的清谈，哼——”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这些鸡就是榜样。”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“既然无人反对，此事理成定局，我战飞此刻就先参见未来江南绿林道的总瓩把子‘裴玸’裴大先生了。”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "“此事固然已成定局，但战兄你却忘了一事。”",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "“忘了什么？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "“此事乃战兄所创，战兄自然赞成，莫大哥兄弟亦是早已赞成，向帮主此刻亦无反对之意，至于小弟么！”",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "“自然更无话说，只是——”",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "“只是战兄却忘了问问人家自己，是否也赞成此事呢？”",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming_shi",
      "text": "“吴兄，贵友裴兄画得一笔丹青，想必识得字吧？可否以笔代口，问他一问？”",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_shi",
      "speaker_name": "吴鸣世",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "“这个倒无须如此，只要小可一问便知。”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_shi",
      "speaker_name": "吴鸣世",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我是在——”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_shi",
      "speaker_name": "吴鸣世",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这位裴兄真是固执得很，小可向他解释半天，他才答应了。”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“没有参见总瓩把子的人，谁也别想离开这里。”",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_xu_xin",
      "text": "“须新，你下来。”",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_xu_xin",
      "text": "“你可知道方才那些人到哪里去了。”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_xin",
      "speaker_name": "须新",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "“小人——没看到。”",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_xu_xin",
      "text": "“养着你们这些废料，真是无用。”",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_xu_xin",
      "text": "“你呆了一天，快去歇歇吧。”",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_xu_xin",
      "text": "“你身体不好，将这些鸡拿回去煮汤来吃，以后就不会常常想睡觉了。”",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“他们人呢？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "“跟我来。”",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "“那莫氏兄弟若是救转了那姓裴的，姓裴的定然对他感激，日后莫南要说什么话，他也不好意思不听。”",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "“听又怎地？不听又怎地？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "“他听不听莫氏兄弟的话，自然与我无关，可是——哼，要知道‘北斗七煞’兄弟七人，论实力却也不在阁下之下呢。”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "“依那兄之见，又该如何呢？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "“依我之见，我若是你，便找一个能助你一臂的帮手，两人同心，力能断金，‘神手’战飞聪明一世，难道会糊涂一时吗？”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "“正是，正是！”",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "“其实小弟早有结交那兄之意，只是难以启口而已，此刻那兄既如此说，想必是肯折节下交的了。”",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "“那姓裴的伤势并不甚重，绝不会伤了性命，可只凭那姓莫的兄弟两人，却绝对治不好他。依我之见，战兄也不必太快将他的伤治愈，也不要说出伤势的轻重来，先拖一段时期再说，若是这姓裴的表示很买我们的账的样子，战兄再将他治愈，也不算迟，否则——哼——”",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "“就想办法把他宰了。”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "“那兄之计，真是妙绝人寰，只怕张良复生，诸葛在世也不过如此，小弟一介武夫，日后还要那兄时常赐教才是。”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "“这个自然。”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "“到了。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这种药怎治得了病！”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“不知道骨头碎了没有？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "神秘女子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“谁是‘北斗七煞’中的老大、老五，统统给我滚出来！”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    }
  ],
